posting_body: ['Meridian Pointe', '251 McAndrews Road West, Burnsville, MN, 55337', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 9', 'OR Text', '9', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to Meridian Pointe', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 762 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Meridian Pointe offers the best value in apartment living in the Burnsville, MN area, just south of downtown Minneapolis/St. Paul.', 'We are committed to your comfort and convenience.', 'Enjoy prompt service from our professional staff.', 'Benefit from our extraordinary features including two natural ponds on the beautifully landscaped property, heated underground parking, a clubhouse with a fitness center, a basketball court, and a sparkling swimming pool.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly!', 'No weight limit, $375 (non-refundable) pet fee.', '$100 (non-refundable) pet fee for the 2nd pet.', '*Breed restrictions apply.', 'We do not permit Pit Bulls (includes Bull Terriers & American Staffordshire Terrier), Rottweilers, German Shepherds, Huskies, Alaskan Malamutes, Doberman Pinchers, Chows, Presa Canaria, Boxers, Dalmatians, Mastiff, American Bulldog, Tosa Ken, Great Danes, Akitas, Wolf Hybrids, Fila Brasileiros or any mix of the previous breeds, or any other dog or breed deemed aggressive by Senior Management.', 'See management for pet approval and deposit and fee information.', '.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.', 'Tuesday: 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.', 'Wednesday: 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.', 'Thursday: 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.', 'Friday: 10:00 a.m. - 6:00 p.m.', 'Saturday: 10:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m.', 'Sunday: Closed', 'rEnFosngV4']
